  "texts": [
    "AI revolutionizes threat hunting by leveraging its predictive capabilities to improve threat detection and identification.",
    "By efficiently processing and analyzing vast amounts of data, AI can recognize meaningful patterns and eliminate irrelevant noise.",
    "Incorporating behavioral analysis into AI enables a more dynamic approach to threat detection, as AI systems can process extensive endpoint data within an organization's network, thus providing comprehensive application profiles that offer insights into normal operational patterns.• Anomaly detection-Anomaly detection plays a critical role in cybersecurity by identifying patterns or behaviors that deviate from the norm within a system.",
    "AI and ML techniques have been instrumental in enhancing the capabilities of anomaly detection systems, enabling them to detect previously unknown threats and adapt to changing attack patterns.",
    "Unsupervised machine learning, in particular, is a popular AI technique for anomaly detection."
